## Validation & Quality

Developer Kit includes a comprehensive validation system:

```bash
# Validate all components
python .skills-validator-check/validators/cli.py --all

# Security scan (MCP compliance)
make security-scan

# Pre-commit hooks
.skills-validator-check/install-hooks.sh
```

